      • propertyFlash

        public CalculationResult propertyFlash​(List<Double> Spec1,
                                       List<Double> Spec2,
                                       int FlashMode,
                                       List<String> components,
                                       List<List<Double>> onlineFractions)
        Perform flashes and return System properties per set of Spec1 and Spec2. Possible to specify fractions for each value of Spec1.
        Parameters:
        Spec1 - Flash pressure in bar absolute.
        Spec2 - Flash specification. Depends on FlashMode. Temperature in Kelvin, entalphy in J/mol or entropy in J/molK.
        FlashMode - 1 - PT 2 - PH 3 - PS
        components - Not yet in use.
        onlineFractions - Specify fractions per sample instance or null to use static composition specified in system.
        Returns:
        Object CalculationResult object
